data.description:
Don't miss this amazing interest rate on 
this very charming home!! Located in a convenient location just a walk away from downtown Anoka! In 2018 about 80% of the home has been completely redone! All new in 2019: roof, trusses, plywood sheeting, gutters, soffit/facia, all new vinyl siding with insulation barrier wrap, all new windows (except north bedroom and bathroom), new carpet and linoleum, all new kitchen cabinets, countertops, all new stainless steel appliances, new front door & garage door, living room hardwood floors refinished, new electrical box and mostly new wiring, new insulation, new garage, 2 more bedrooms added. New deck in 2020 and this year they've added new fencing to the side patio which offers privacy and tranquility. Plus there's an amazing 11 x 8 'garden shed' in the front. Convenient main floor Laundry along with all living facilities on one level! Dining room buffet cabinet can be included in sale. A must-see! Book your showing today!
